  <brief_title>Phase II Evaluating Endoresection of the Tumor Scar or Transpupillary Thermotherapy When Endoresection is Not Feasible After Proton Beam Therapy for the Treatment of Large Uveal Melanomas (Endoresection-Laser)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Evaluating Endoresection of the Tumor Scar or Transpupillary Thermotherapy When Endoresection is Not Feasible After Proton Beam Therapy for the Treatment of Large Uveal Melanomas</official_title>
