  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study the efficacy of endoresection of the tumor scar or, when surgery is not possible,
      transpupillary thermotherapy on the tumor scar to prevent neovascular glaucoma and secondary
      enucleation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
